  "description": "Rapid-cycling annual from Brassicaceae, native to western Mediterranean and North Africa. Extremely fast germination and development (15–20 days); produces peppery, glucosinolate-rich seedlings and young leaves. Bolts quickly but allows many successive plantings in a season.",
